---

<BaseLayout
  title="Best Cafe Near Nashville | 45 Minutes to Centerville | The Local Place"
  description="Looking for a quality cafe near Nashville? The Local Place in Centerville is 45 minutes south. Specialty coffee, fresh food, homemade ice cream. Worth the drive."
  keywords="cafe near Nashville, coffee shop Nashville area, breakfast near Nashville, lunch cafe Nashville"
>
  <!-- Schema markup placeholder for LocalBusiness -->
  <!-- TODO: Add JSON-LD schema for location-specific business info -->

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>Cafe Near Nashville Worth the Drive</h1>
      <p>45 Minutes South. Real Coffee, Fresh Food, Homemade Ice Cream</p>
      <a href="https://www.clover.com/online-ordering/the-local-place-centerville-2" class="hero-cta">Order Online</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container py-4">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <ol>
        <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
        <li><span>Cafe Near Nashville</span></li>
      </ol>
    </nav>

    <section class="location-intro">
      <h2>45 Minutes South of Nashville</h2>
      <p>
        Tired of overpriced Nashville cafes where the coffee tastes burnt and the pastries came from a truck? Drive 45 minutes south to Centerville and find something better—a locally owned cafe where the coffee is pulled fresh, the pastries are baked in-house, and the ice cream is made here.
      </p>
      <p>
        This isn't a chain. It's not trying to be Instagram-perfect. It's a real cafe with real food, real coffee, and people who actually care whether you leave satisfied.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="location-content">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <div class="content-block">
          <h3>Easy Drive from Nashville</h3>
          <p><strong>Distance:</strong> 45 minutes south of Nashville</p>
          <p><strong>Route:</strong> I-40 West → US-100 South → Centerville</p>
          <p><strong>Address:</strong> 111 South Public Square, Centerville, TN 37033</p>
          <p><strong>Parking:</strong> Free parking around the square</p>
          <p>
            Straight shot from Nashville. Leave the traffic, the crowds, and the overpriced mediocrity behind. Come to a place where coffee tastes like coffee and food is made fresh.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <h3>Perfect for Nashville Visitors</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Weekend breakfast:</strong> Escape the city, grab a real breakfast sandwich and fresh coffee</li>
            <li><strong>Day trips:</strong> Stop for lunch on your way to exploring Centerville</li>
            <li><strong>Remote work escape:</strong> Drive out, set up your laptop, enjoy good coffee and Wi-Fi</li>
            <li><strong>Date day:</strong> Coffee, lunch, ice cream—better than another Nashville brunch spot</li>
            <li><strong>Family outing:</strong> Kids love the homemade ice cream, adults love the real food</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <h3>What We Serve</h3>
          <p><strong>Specialty Coffee:</strong> Espresso, lattes, cappuccinos, cold brew. Fresh-pulled, not burnt.</p>
          <p><strong>Breakfast:</strong> Sandwiches, bagels, breakfast plates. Open 6am weekdays, 9am Saturdays.</p>
          <p><strong>Lunch:</strong> Paninis, wraps, salads, soups. Made to order, hot and fresh.</p>
          <p><strong>Pastries:</strong> House-made croissants, muffins, scones, cinnamon rolls. Baked daily.</p>
          <p><strong>Ice Cream:</strong> Homemade, rotating flavors. Creamy, rich, better than any chain.</p>
          <p><strong>Smoothies & Drinks:</strong> Real fruit smoothies, iced drinks, specialty beverages.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content-block">
          <h3>Why Nashville People Make the Drive</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Real coffee, not burnt corporate shots</li>
            <li>Pastries baked in-house, not trucked in frozen</li>
            <li>Homemade ice cream you can't get anywhere else</li>
            <li>Fresh lunch made to order</li>
            <li>Comfortable seating, good Wi-Fi, no rush</li>
            <li>Locally owned, not a franchise</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonials">
      <h2>Why Nashville People Visit</h2>
      <div class="testimonial-cards">
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"We drove from East Nashville for brunch. The croissant was flaky, the latte was perfect, and the vibe was relaxed. Way better than waiting an hour at some crowded Nashville spot."</p>
          <p><strong>- Emma & Jake (Nashville)</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"I work remote and needed a change of scenery. Drove out here, set up my laptop, ordered a few coffees throughout the day. Wi-Fi's fast, coffee's good, nobody bothered me."</p>
          <p><strong>- Marcus (Nashville Remote Worker)</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial-card">
          <p>"My kids begged to come back after we tried the ice cream. It's homemade, creamy, and way better than anything in Nashville. Now it's a monthly trip for us."</p>
          <p><strong>- The Patterson Family (Franklin/Nashville area)</strong></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="faq-section">
      <h2>Questions from Nashville Visitors</h2>
      <div class="faq-items">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>How long is the drive from Nashville?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              About 45 minutes from downtown Nashville. Take I-40 West, exit onto US-100 South toward Centerville. We're on the square at 111 South Public Square.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Is it worth the drive?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              If you're tired of paying $7 for burnt coffee and stale pastries, yeah. You'll get real coffee, house-made food, and homemade ice cream. Plus, you're supporting a local business, not a chain.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Can I work here on my laptop?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              Yes. Free Wi-Fi, comfortable seating, and we're not going to kick you out after 30 minutes. Order coffee, set up, get work done. Just be respectful during busy times.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Can I order ahead?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              Yes. Order online through Clover and it'll be ready when you arrive. Perfect if you're driving out and don't want to wait.
            </p>
            <p><a href="https://www.clover.com/online-ordering/the-local-place-centerville-2" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #8b4513; font-weight: 600;">Order on Clover →</a></p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>What are your hours?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              Monday-Friday: 6 AM - 6 PM<br />
              Saturday: 9 AM - 6 PM<br />
              Sunday: Closed
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>

        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary class="faq-question">
            <span>Is it kid-friendly?</span>
            <span class="toggle-icon">+</span>
          </summary>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>
              Absolutely. We serve ice cream, smoothies, breakfast—kids love it here. Families are welcome.
            </p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <h2>Ready to Escape Nashville?</h2>
      <p>
        Order online or just show up. We're here six days a week, ready with fresh coffee, real food, and homemade ice cream.
      </p>
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; gap: 1rem; display: flex; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="https://www.clover.com/online-ordering/the-local-place-centerville-2" class="cta-button">Order Online</a>
        <a href="tel:(931)729-3481" class="cta-button">Call (931) 729-3481</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="location-info">
      <h2>Visit The Local Place Cafe</h2>
      <div class="info-grid">
        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>Hours</h3>
          <p>
            <strong>Monday-Friday:</strong> 6 AM - 6 PM<br />
            <strong>Saturday:</strong> 9 AM - 6 PM<br />
            <strong>Sunday:</strong> Closed
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>Location</h3>
          <p>
            111 South Public Square<br />
            Centerville, TN 37033<br />
            <strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:(931)729-3481">(931) 729-3481</a>
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="info-block">
          <h3>From Nashville</h3>
          <p>
            45 minutes south via I-40 W → US-100 S<br />
            Free parking around the square
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .hero {
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)), url('/hero-bg.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    text-align: center;
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: white;
  }

  .hero-content p {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: var(--brown);
    color: white;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .hero-cta:hover {
    background-color: var(--red);
  }

  .location-intro {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .location-intro h2 {
    color: var(--brown);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .location-intro p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .content-block {
    background: white;
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--brown);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .content-block h3 {
    color: var(--brown);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }

  .content-block p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .content-block ul {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 2rem;
  }

  .content-block li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .testimonials {
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .testimonials h2 {
    color: var(--brown);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .testimonial-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--brown);
  }

  .testimonial-card p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .testimonial-card p:first-child {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }

  .testimonial-card p strong {
    color: var(--brown);
  }

  .faq-section {
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .faq-section h2 {
    color: var(--brown);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .faq-items {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: white;
  }

  .faq-question {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: var(--light-gray);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark);
    user-select: none;
  }

  .faq-question:hover {
    background: #efefef;
  }

  .toggle-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-item[open] .toggle-icon {
    transform: rotate(45deg);
  }

  .faq-answer {
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
  }

  .faq-answer p {
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .cta-section {
    background: var(--light-gray);
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 4rem 0;
  }

  .cta-section h2 {
    color: var(--brown);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: var(--brown);
    color: white;
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    background-color: var(--red);
  }

  .location-info {
    margin-top: 3rem;
  }

  .info-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 2rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .info-block {
    background: var(--cream);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #8b4513;
  }

  .info-block h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    color: var(--dark);
  }

  .info-block p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .info-block a {
    color: var(--brown);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .info-block a:hover {
    color: var(--red);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .hero-content p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .content-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .info-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
